Task: Create LessonCard component

Summary: Implemented LessonCard component for displaying lesson metadata with completion status.

Changes:
- Created components/student/LessonCard.tsx with:
  - Lesson number and title display
  - Phase count (with proper singular/plural handling)
  - Completion status indicator (Completed/Not started)
  - Visual styling differences for completed vs. not completed states
  - Green border for completed lessons
  - Hover effects for interactive feedback
  - Proper ARIA labels for accessibility
- Updated components/student/index.ts to export LessonCard
- Created comprehensive test suite (__tests__/components/student/LessonCard.test.tsx) with 11 tests covering:
  - Lesson metadata rendering (number, title, phase count)
  - Link behavior and href
  - Completion status display and styling
  - Accessibility (ARIA labels)
  - Edge cases (single phase, many phases)

Why: Lesson cards are the primary way students navigate through course content. They provide at-a-glance information about lesson progress and encourage continued learning.

Files created/modified:
- components/student/LessonCard.tsx (new)
- components/student/index.ts (modified)
- __tests__/components/student/LessonCard.test.tsx (new)
